<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id80e33db3-3a70-11f1-b817-c08bf6d1fe2c" identifier="/us/usc/t40/s14704"><num value="14704">§ 14704.</num><heading> Termination</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">This subtitle, except sections 14102(a)(1) and (b) and 14501, ceases to be in effect on <date date="2026-10-01">October 1, 2026</date>.</p>
